sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Gets future date time from current date. Calculated from current data time to the number of days specified in configurations record field - "Number of days to look ahead for upcoming onboarding and offboarding events".

Outputs:

  • Future Date - Future Date.
  • Future Date Time - Future Date and Time.
